  "about_item": [
    "Reversible Design for Double the Style: This innovative dog anxiety vest is made to be worn two ways, offering a fresh look and extended durability. The reversible thunder shirt for dogs means you can choose the color that best suits your mood or situation, providing versatile calming support for storms, vet visits, or separation",
    "Plush & Elastic Fleece for Ultimate Comfort: Crafted from high-quality 90% polyester, 10% spandex fleece, this dog calming vest is incredibly soft, thick, and offers comfortable stretch in all directions. The plush, skin-friendly fabric ensures your pet stays cozy and soothed without feeling restricted, making it a comfortable anxiety relief jacket for all-day wear. Light-weight, breathable, and machine washable for easy care",
    "Find the Perfect Fit for Your Dog: Available in six sizes (XS to 2XL), this dog calming shirt fits small medium large and extra large dogs. Measure your dog before ordering to ensure this thunder shirt provides optimal comfort and anxiety relief. This dog hoodie suit for indoor or outdoor occasions such as dog grooming, walking, bathing, home cleaning, hurricanes, photo shoot and other events",
    "Adjustable Turtleneck with Soothing Ear Wrap: The versatile collar on this thunder shirt can be worn as a turtleneck for extra warmth or folded down. For maximum calming, it can be gently pulled up to cover your dog's ears, creating a secure, hug-like effect that helps muffle frightening noises from fireworks or thunderstorms",
    "Wider Straps for a Secure, Custom Fit: Calming Wrap for Dogs features extra-wide hook-and-loop straps that are easy to fasten and adjust, eaay to put on/off, significantly increasing the belly coverage for a more enveloping, calming pressure. This anxiety vest allows you to customize the snugness for a perfect and secure fit that effectively comforts your dog"
  ],
