      {
        "position": 3,
        "title": "Fit is important on this style. Very soft and easy to get on.",
        "text": "This was a soft item and the neck part fit really well but the body section was too big and not enough Velcro adjustment to fit tighter on my dog. I know my doggie does not like things tight around her neck and I did not want to get one too small. She is a 6-lb chiweenie and this neck/head part worked for her. It was easy to get on since the head/neck was not too tight. The fabric felt good and comfy. She did not like the turtle neck pulled up around her ears really. This might work for some dogs but not so much for mine due to the fit and her not liking it over her ears. She did not mind the neck being folded for a turtle neck as it was comfortable. Be sure you get sizing right.",
        "rating": 3,
        "date": "October 21, 2025",
