      {
        "position": 4,
        "title": "Better than the original thunder shirt",
        "text": "So I loved the idea of having a piece of clothing for my dog to wear that would help with thunder and anxiety. My dog does not care if its thundering or not but does have major separation anxiety. Since his anxiety only happens whenI am away from him it is hard to gauge how well this shirt works.I will say that the material is nice and soft, the price isn't bad and the design is nice since its easy to put on and take off.The only thing I will say is that it seems to run a little bit small. I know its supposed to be tight but I think I would have been better ordering the next size up.All in all I think it's a smart idea and worth a shot if your pup suffers from anxiety.",
