      {
        "position": 7,
        "title": "Nicer than expected!",
        "text": "The material is soft and pretty thick.The vest itself feels to be of really good quality, better than I had expected for the price.I like that it is fairly adjustable, with the ability to tighten it with the Velcro straps. Dogs have varying shapes and sizes beyond just small, medium, large, etc.., and it’s nice that it’s been realized here.Obviously, this isn’t a product that will work to calm every animal, but if these types of shirts/vests do work for your pet, or you’d like to give them a try, this is not a bad one to try out!It’s good quality for the price, it’s adjustable, and it has the turtleneck option.I wasn’t sure if my little guy would like the turtleneck thing, but I’m happy I tried it out. Definitely satisfied with the whole thing!",
